as an aside A simple Spoken Python example

open function greet parameters with name
    let greeting be enchant with string Hello variable name
    print with greeting
close function greet

open function factorial parameters with n
    open if n is less than or equal to 1
        return 1
    close if
    return n times factorial with n minus 1
close function factorial

as an aside Main program
greet with string literal World
let result be factorial with 5
print with result
